organizations and all sectors. The complaints-handling process is suitable to implement as one of the processes of an overall quality management system. ISO 10002 standard helps to identify the complaints, their cause and how to rectify the complaints effectively and efficiently."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700","children":"ISO 10002 assists the companies to take the complaints about their product from the unsatisfied customers and in turn to improve the quality of the product for the future customers. The current version of ISO 10002 certification is the ISO 10002:2014. It will be reviewed and replaced by the ISO 10002:2019."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"Ways to implement ISO 10002 certification in your company"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 mb-4","children":"ISO 10002 Certification can be implemented in five steps. Also, ISO 10002 checklist is listed below:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-2","children":[["$","li",null,{"className":"flex gap-3 items-start","children":[["$","svg",null,{"stroke":"currentColor","fill":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"0","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","className":"text-rose-600 shrink-0 mt-1 text-lg","children":["$undefined",[["$","path","0",{"fill":"none","d":"M0 0h24v24H0z","children":[]}],["$","path","1",{"d":"M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z","children":[]}]]],"style":{"color":"$undefined"},"height":"1em","width":"1em","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-gray-700","children":["Choose the ",["$","$Lf",null,{"href":"/","className":"text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800","children":"best ISO 10002 Certification consultant in Dubai"}]," and rest of UAE."]}]]}],["$","li",null,{"className":"flex gap-3 items-start","children":["$L10","$L11"]}],"$L12","$L13","$L14","$L15","$L16"]}]]}],"$L17","$L18